data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in a vibrant community. This single-story residence boasts an open concept layout with split bedrooms, offering both privacy and togetherness. Enjoy the convenience of ceiling fans in every room, while the eat-in kitchen with a walk-in pantry provides ample space for culinary adventures. The primary suite features a separate tub and shower, ensuring a peaceful retreat separate from the other rooms. Outside, the community amenities include two playgrounds, a refreshing pool, a basketball court, and a scenic walking trail. With its proximity to shopping centers and dining options, this home epitomizes comfort, convenience, and a welcoming community feel.
In Keller ISD
